overview:
Nell Terry is freelance writer specializing in Internet marketing, tech news, and SEO. She holds both a BA and an MPA, which allows her to bring an educated perspective to her work. She is a staff blogger for several well-known blogs in the industry. You can find out more about her work by visiting her writer’s website at ContentbyNell.com.
